# Frontend rules

## Entry point

`src/main.jsx` routes by URL path — **no router library**:
- `/pricing` → `<PricingPage />`
- `/stack/{id}` → `<AgeGate /> + <PublicStackView shareId />`
- `/profile/{handle}` → `<AgeGate /> + <PublicMemberProfilePage handle />`
- else → `<AppErrorBoundary><App /></AppErrorBoundary>`

## Shell tree

```
<PepGuideIQ>  (default export of App.jsx, line 2687)
  ├── <AgeGate /> (if !ageVerified)
  ├── <AuthScreen /> (if !user)
  └── <ProfileProvider userId plan>
       └── <DoseToastProvider>
            └── <TutorialProvider>
                 └── <PepGuideIQApp>  (holds the giant state surface, line 386)
                      └── <PepGuideIQMainTree>  (line 1207)
                           ├── Header: <Logo /> <ProfileSwitcher /> <NotificationsBell />
                           ├── Tab content (one of 8)
                           ├── <NavTooltips />
                           └── <DoseLogFAB />
```

## Context providers and hooks

| Provider | Hook | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `ProfileContext` | `useActiveProfile()` | member_profiles list + active profile id. Throws outside provider. |
| `DoseToastContext` | `useShowDoseToast()` | Post-log toast. No-op outside provider. |
| `TutorialContext` | `useTutorial()` / `useTutorialOptional()` | Onboarding tour. Highlights via `data-tutorial-target` + `tutorialHighlightProps()`. |

## State conventions

- `useState` grouped thematically at the top of component functions.
- **No `useReducer` anywhere in the codebase.**
- **No Redux, Zustand, Jotai, MobX.**
- Cross-tab data lives in `ProfileContext` or is lifted into `PepGuideIQApp`.

## Styling

- Inline `style={{...}}` objects.
- Global classes in `GlobalStyles.jsx`: `brand`, `mono`, `btn-red`, `btn-teal`, `form-input`, `scard`, `pcard`, `pill--category`, `search-input`.
- Category colors from `CAT_COLORS` in `src/data/catalog.js`. Use `getCategoryCssVars(cat)` to set `--cc` and `--cc-rgb` custom properties.
- **Design system:** Read `DESIGN.md` at the repo root before building or modifying any UI component. Use its color tokens, spacing scale, and component patterns. Never introduce colors, fonts, or spacing values not defined there.

## Storage keys (don't collide)

| Key | Storage | Shape |
|---|---|---|
| `pepv_age_verified_v2` | localStorage | `{t: number, v: 1}` |
| `pepv_age_verified` | localStorage | legacy boolean fallback |
| `pepguide_ref` | localStorage | affiliate ref string |
| `pepv_last_tab` | sessionStorage | tab id string |
| `pepguideiq.active_profile_id.{userId}` | localStorage | member_profile uuid |

